SUMMARY:Raina Haq [@rxh]
DESCRIPTION:<2026-03-26 Thu 13:30-17:00>\n• test new monomer M2a.\n• checke
 d "flip" approach but this won't work because transcription\n  will be of 
 the complement of M1\, which is not the desired protein.\n  So we need the
  *complement of M2* to be correct without mistakes.\n  In fact\, M1 can to
 lerate mismatches since it is not being\n  transcribed.
